      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0635P0-03508'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0635P0_20020523_GCR_69' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 15 [<span class="italic">Revised provisional decisions after notifications</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0635P0-03509'>
